data.description:
Welcome to your dream residence, where luxury and comfort converge in a two-story traditional masterpiece. As you step through the front door, the open-concept floorplan beckons, boasting soaring ceilings that create an airy and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen, a culinary haven, features a large breakfast bar and a gas cooktop & range hood set in stunning stone. Enjoy meals in the breakfast nook surrounded by windows that seamlessly connect to the living room, where a gas fireplace adds warmth and charm to every moment.
Wood floors grace the office and the spacious primary bedroom on the main level, complemented by a grand ensuite bathroom and an ample closet. Upstairs, the entertainment hub awaits with a versatile gameroom, a guest suite featuring its own ensuite, and two secondary bedrooms offering comfort and flexibility for your lifestyle.
However, the true allure of this home extends beyond its interior. Venture outside to discover a backyard oasis designed for relaxation and entertainment. Multiple levels of seating, including a covered patio, an expansive deck, and a charming sitting area beneath a pergola, surround the heated pool with a cascading waterfall and a luxurious hot tub. As the sun sets, the gas fire pit by the pool creates an enchanting ambiance, turning the outdoor space into a magical retreat.
Before you leave, savor a moment on the covered front porch, surrounded by rich landscaping that adorns the front yard, enhancing the home's curb appeal. This residence is not just a house; it's a harmonious blend of indoor elegance and outdoor splendor, offering a lifestyle that seamlessly combines modern living with timeless charm. Make this property yours and experience the epitome of San Antonio living, where every detail has been thoughtfully curated to create a haven you'll be proud to call home.
